  "id": "RAW_dd3f21ac",
  "title": "动画师与 AI 研究员如何共同创作《亲爱的楼上邻居》",
  "url": "https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/models-and-research/google-deepmind/dear-upstairs-neighbors/",
  "date": "2026-01-26 18:00:00",
  "author": "Cassidy Curtis",
  "siteName": "The Keyword (blog.google) ",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"audio-player-tts\" data-component=\"uni-audio-player-tts\" uni-l10n=\"{\n       &quot;stop&quot;: &quot;Click to stop audio&quot;,\n       &quot;play&quot;: &quot;Click to play audio&quot;,\n       &quot;progress&quot;: &quot;Current audio progress minutes with seconds: [[progress]]&quot;,\n       &quot;duration&quot;: &quot;Duration of the audio minutes with seconds: [[duration]]&quot;,\n       &quot;settings&quot;: &quot;Click for settings&quot;,\n       &quot;timeText&quot;: &quot;[[duration]] minutes&quot;\n     }\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n      &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Audio TTS&quot;,\n      &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’&quot;\n     }\" data-tts-audios=\"[\n      \n        {&quot;voice_name&quot;: &quot;Gacrux&quot;,\n        &quot;voice_source&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/media/tts_audio_83165_gacrux_2026_01_26_18_03_47.wav&quot;,\n        &quot;mimetype&quot;: &quot;audio/x-wav&quot;},\n      \n        {&quot;voice_name&quot;: &quot;Umbriel&quot;,\n        &quot;voice_source&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/media/tts_audio_83165_umbriel_2026_01_26_18_04_33.wav&quot;,\n        &quot;mimetype&quot;: &quot;audio/x-wav&quot;}\n      ]\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n   <audio class=\"audio-player-tts__player\" title=\"How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’\">\n    <source src=\"https://blog.google/self.ttsaudio_set.first.tts_audio.url\" type=\"self.ttsaudio_set.first.tts_audio.file.file.mime_type\">\n    <p>Your browser does not support the audio element.</p>\n   </audio>\n   <div class=\"audio-player-tts__container\" aria-label=\"\">\n    <div class=\"audio-player-tts__content\">\n     <button class=\"audio-player-tts__preview-play\" aria-label=\"Click to play audio\">\n      <svg class=\"icon audio-player-tts__play-icon\">\n       <use xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20260120-1609#ttf-play-spark\"></use>\n      </svg>\n     </button>\n     <div class=\"audio-player-tts__text-content\">\n      <br>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"audio-player-tts__console\">\n      <div class=\"audio-player-tts__settings-container\"></div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"yxfsj\" class=\"drop-cap\">Today, our animated short film, “Dear Upstairs Neighbors,” previews at the Sundance Film Festival. The film will be showcased at the Sundance Institute’s Story Forum, a space focused on artist-first tools and technologies supporting visual storytelling.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"34ve\">“Dear Upstairs Neighbors” is the story of a young woman, Ada, who is desperate for a good night’s sleep but kept awake by her exceedingly noisy neighbors. As she struggles to imagine what could be causing the cacophony upstairs, reality drifts into fantasy, and an epic battle for peace and sanity ensues.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"bgdqn\">The film is a collaboration between <a href=\"https://www.imdb.com/title/tt39368604/reference\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">animation veterans</a>, including director and Pixar alum Connie He, and researchers at Google DeepMind, united by a shared goal of exploring how generative tools might fit in with artists' creative processes.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-carousel section-header=\"How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Figure01_storyboard_montage.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A video of storyboards, drawn in a loose but expressive style, visualizing Ada’s experience of annoying sounds (including an electric guitar, a gong, a drill, and a vacuum cleaner) as if those things were literally happening to her.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Figure01_storyboard_montage.mp4&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure02_character_turnaround.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure02_character_turnaround.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A series of handmade paintings showing Ada, a young woman in her pyjamas with curly blue\\u002Dblack hair in a messy bun, standing in a neutral pose, rendered from several different angles.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure03_DUN_Expression_color.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure03_DUN_Expression_color.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A series of paintings showing Ada’s face with a variety of extreme expressions: joy, rage, fear, wonder, yawning, and many more.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure03a_Ada_bedroom_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure03a_Ada_bedroom_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A painting of Ada’s bedroom, showing the arrangement of her bed, desk, bookshelves, and various objects, rendered in isometric perspective with a cool color palette.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure04_Log_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure04_Log_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A painting of a saw cutting a log, in vivid neon turquoise, magenta and yellow on a black background.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure05_700_6_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure05_700_6_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A painting of Ada standing on her bed, enraged by all the noise, her mouth in an angry grimace, her hands balled into fists, and red and orange flames bursting out from her in all directions.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure06_700_8_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Figure06_700_8_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;An expressionistic painting of a giant speaker floating menacingly above a mysterious landscape, in garish tones of black, red, and yellow.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      }\n    \n  ]\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"article-module ga4-carousel\" data-component=\"uni-image-carousel\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Article Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’&quot;}\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"article-carousel\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\">\n     <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"carousel-item-1769457877534\" data-slider-height-loaded=\"true\" style=\"height: 363.875px;\">\n      <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide article-carousel__slide--active\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1769457877534-0\" aria-label=\"1 of 7\" style=\"left: 0%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n         <div class=\"article-carousel__slide-img article-carousel__video-slide\">\n          <uni-video-player custom-class=\"article-carousel__media\" muted playsinline=\"\" controls=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" alt-text=\"A video of storyboards, drawn in a loose but expressive style, visualizing Ada’s experience of annoying sounds (including an electric guitar, a gong, a drill, and a vacuum cleaner) as if those things were literally happening to her.\" autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" tts-json=\"[]\" section-header=\"How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’\" video-url=\" https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Figure01_storyboard_montage.mp4 \" video-title=\"Figure01_storyboard_montage.mp4\" audio-descripted-video=\"\">\n           <!---->\n           <div class=\"uni-video-player\">\n            <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n            <video crossorigin=\"anonymous\" preload=\"metadata\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"A video of storyboards, drawn in a loose but expressive style, visualizing Ada’s experience of annoying sounds (including an electric guitar, a gong, a drill, and a vacuum cleaner) as if those things were literally happening to her.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Figure01_storyboard_montage.mp4#t=0.001\" class=\" uni-video-player__video uni-video-player__video--autoplay article-carousel__media \" title=\"Figure01_storyboard_montage.mp4\" style=\"min-height:0px;\" autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" poster=\"\">\n             Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a download=\"\" href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Figure01_storyboard_montage.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n            </video>\n            <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n           </div>\n          </uni-video-player>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-0\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"vl2qa\">Director Connie He developed the story based on her personal experience with noisy neighbors. In her storyboards she envisioned a series of hallucinations that get more unhinged and ridiculous as the night progresses.</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877534-0\" data-index=\"1\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877534-1\" data-index=\"2\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877534-2\" data-index=\"3\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877534-3\" data-index=\"4\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 4</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877534-4\" data-index=\"5\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 5</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877534-5\" data-index=\"6\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 6</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877534-6\" data-index=\"7\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 7</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"yxfsj\">From the start, the team aspired to empower animation artists to benefit from the creative potential of generative AI without sacrificing artistic control to its inherent unpredictability. To define her vision for this film, Connie developed the storyboards, and enlisted award-winning production designer Yingzong Xin to create concept art and character designs. We committed to staying faithful to this artistic vision throughout shot production.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"qqro\">The expressionistic visual styles are central to the storytelling — and extremely difficult to achieve in traditional animation. We expected that AI could help fill the gap, but soon found that these styles were so unique, and our design choices so specific, that our researchers would have to develop new capabilities to provide the customization and control that we needed to bring the film to life.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"yxfsj\">Tune for new visual styles</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"egnhl\">Our first challenge was to produce shots consistent with Ada’s character design and the painterly styles that defined each scene. To achieve high quality and consistency, our researchers built tools that allowed our artists to fine-tune custom Veo and Imagen models on their artwork, teaching the models new visual concepts from just a few example images.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-carousel section-header=\"How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM_AdaT2I_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM_AdaT2I_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A grid of twelve colorful painterly images of Ada in a variety of situations: swimming, rock climbing, boxing, playing soccer, DJing, playing with kids in a waterfall, gazing in wonder at the aurora in an arctic landscape, and more.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure08_sq200_video_v04_1_2.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A video showing stylized magenta and blue concept paintings of shoes, a sofa, and a log on the left, and on the right a series of video clips of roller skates, trees, a man walking, and a person lifting weights, all of which match the paintings in color palette, brush texture, and perspective.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Figure08_sq200_video_v04 (1).mp4&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure09_AdaSpin.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A video showing a series of static paintings of Ada’s face at the top, a rotating 3D computer graphics model of Ada’s head in the lower left, and a painterly, stylized version of Ada’s rotating head in the lower right.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Figure09_AdaSpin (1).mp4&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      }\n    \n  ]\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"article-module ga4-carousel\" data-component=\"uni-image-carousel\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Article Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’&quot;}\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"article-carousel\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\">\n     <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"carousel-item-1769457877535\" data-slider-height-loaded=\"true\" style=\"height: 435.875px;\">\n      <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide article-carousel__slide--active\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1769457877535-0\" aria-label=\"1 of 3\" style=\"left: 0%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n         <img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 32px), (min-width: 768px and max-width: 1024px) 800px, 565px\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"article-carousel__img\" srcset=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM_AdaT2I_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 800w, https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM_AdaT2I_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 1600w\" alt=\"A grid of twelve colorful painterly images of Ada in a variety of situations: swimming, rock climbing, boxing, playing soccer, DJing, playing with kids in a waterfall, gazing in wonder at the aurora in an arctic landscape, and more.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM_AdaT2I_1080p.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp\">\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-0\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"d8hvv\">Images of Ada generated by Imagen after fine-tuning. The fine-tuned model helped the whole team explore Ada as a character.</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877535-0\" data-index=\"1\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877535-1\" data-index=\"2\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877535-2\" data-index=\"3\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"yxfsj\">Show, don’t type</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"cbiib\">Another challenge was precisely controlling the content and motion of each shot. We knew that text prompting alone would never let us control the rhythm of Ada’s sleepy fingers typing, the comedic timing of her facial expressions, or the exact framing of a camera reveal. We needed a way to communicate that level of nuance and specificity to our AI models. Our researchers drew inspiration from how our animators communicate visually, by drawing, painting or acting out scenes. We developed novel video-to-video workflows, which allowed our animators to convey their intentions visually by creating rough animation in their tool of choice. Our models then transformed that animation into fully stylized videos that follow the input motion, with an adjustable balance between tight control and creative improvisation.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-carousel section-header=\"How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure10_Bloopers_Spaghetti.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A series of video scenes showing Ada eating spaghetti, often doing so in a way that violates the laws of physics, not to mention decorum.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Figure10_Bloopers_Spaghetti.mp4&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure11_HappyAda_Montage.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A video showing unlit and untextured 3D animation of Ada happily collapsing into bed, which transitions into a second video showing the same scene with moody blue lighting and a rough, hand\\u002Dpainted aesthetic.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Figure11_HappyAda_Montage.mp4&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure12_ChaosMontage_Short.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;At left, three paintings in vivid neon pink, yellow, turquoise and purple, depicting Ada’s sound\\u002Dbased hallucinations\\u003B at right, a black\\u002Dand\\u002Dwhite video of hand\\u002Ddrawn 2D animation of Ada experiencing those events, which transitions into a colorful painterly rendition of the scene that matches the palette and style of the paintings.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Figure12_ChaosMontage_Short.mp4&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Figure13_AdaNotes_Montage.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A before\\u002Dand\\u002Dafter video showing 3D animation of Ada running away while being bombarded by musical notes, with rudimentary textures and effects made of simple black shapes, which transitions through a few stages into an expressionist painterly rendition of the same scene, in which the simple shapes have been transformed into lush splatters of colorful paint.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Ada Notes&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      }\n    \n  ]\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"article-module ga4-carousel\" data-component=\"uni-image-carousel\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Article Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’&quot;}\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"article-carousel\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\">\n     <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"carousel-item-1769457877536\" data-slider-height-loaded=\"true\" style=\"height: 387.875px;\">\n      <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide article-carousel__slide--active\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1769457877536-0\" aria-label=\"1 of 4\" style=\"left: 0%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n         <div class=\"article-carousel__slide-img article-carousel__video-slide\">\n          <uni-video-player custom-class=\"article-carousel__media\" muted playsinline=\"\" controls=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" alt-text=\"A series of video scenes showing Ada eating spaghetti, often doing so in a way that violates the laws of physics, not to mention decorum.\" autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" tts-json=\"[]\" section-header=\"How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’\" video-url=\" https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure10_Bloopers_Spaghetti.mp4 \" video-title=\"Figure10_Bloopers_Spaghetti.mp4\" audio-descripted-video=\"\">\n           <!---->\n           <div class=\"uni-video-player\">\n            <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n            <video crossorigin=\"anonymous\" preload=\"metadata\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"A series of video scenes showing Ada eating spaghetti, often doing so in a way that violates the laws of physics, not to mention decorum.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure10_Bloopers_Spaghetti.mp4#t=0.001\" class=\" uni-video-player__video uni-video-player__video--autoplay article-carousel__media \" title=\"Figure10_Bloopers_Spaghetti.mp4\" style=\"min-height:0px;\" autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" poster=\"\">\n             Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a download=\"\" href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure10_Bloopers_Spaghetti.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n            </video>\n            <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n           </div>\n          </uni-video-player>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-0\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"qso9o\">Using text-to-video with the fine-tuned Veo model produced scenes that looked like Ada, but their movement was random, uncontrolled, and often bizarre. Text alone can’t convey the nuance and specificity needed for narrative animated filmmaking.</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877536-0\" data-index=\"1\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877536-1\" data-index=\"2\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877536-2\" data-index=\"3\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877536-3\" data-index=\"4\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 4</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"yxfsj\">Iterate toward perfection</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"63u2r\">Even with the control provided by fine-tuning and video-to-video workflows, none of our final shots were created in a single “one-click” generation. Just as in any film production, we critiqued each shot in our “dailies” reviews, going through several rounds of feedback to get every detail right. To iterate on a shot without re-generating from scratch every time, we built tools for localized refinement, allowing us to edit specific regions of a video with an adjustable level of control.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-carousel section-header=\"How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure14_DogMontage_Short.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A before\\u002Dand\\u002Dafter video showing a concept painting of a blue dog howling, surrounded by magenta brushstrokes, which becomes an animated video of a dog which is at first photorealistic, and then transitions through several stages until it becomes a living painting of a stylized dog.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Figure14_DogMontage_Short.mp4&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure15_DogVariations.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A video showing three different variations of the same howling dog scene, in which the blue dog is the same, but the magenta shapes are different (spikes, circular ripples, and lightning bolts), followed by another trio of scenes with the same action being performed by three different kinds of dog (a sheltie, a borzoi, and a cartoon).&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Figure15_DogVariations.mp4&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure16_AdaAww_Montage.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A 3D animated scene of Ada smiling warmly at her laptop screen, which transitions into a painterly rendition of the same moment. A red shape appears, indicating an area where Ada should have more hair, transitioning into a final version with an extra tuft of hair in that region.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Figure16_AdaAww_Montage.mp4&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      }\n    \n  ]\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"article-module ga4-carousel\" data-component=\"uni-image-carousel\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Article Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’&quot;}\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"article-carousel\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\">\n     <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"carousel-item-1769457877537\" data-slider-height-loaded=\"true\" style=\"height: 411.875px;\">\n      <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide article-carousel__slide--active\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1769457877537-0\" aria-label=\"1 of 3\" style=\"left: 0%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n         <div class=\"article-carousel__slide-img article-carousel__video-slide\">\n          <uni-video-player custom-class=\"article-carousel__media\" muted playsinline=\"\" controls=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" alt-text=\"A before-and-after video showing a concept painting of a blue dog howling, surrounded by magenta brushstrokes, which becomes an animated video of a dog which is at first photorealistic, and then transitions through several stages until it becomes a living painting of a stylized dog.\" autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" tts-json=\"[]\" section-header=\"How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’\" video-url=\" https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure14_DogMontage_Short.mp4 \" video-title=\"Figure14_DogMontage_Short.mp4\" audio-descripted-video=\"\">\n           <!---->\n           <div class=\"uni-video-player\">\n            <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n            <video crossorigin=\"anonymous\" preload=\"metadata\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"A before-and-after video showing a concept painting of a blue dog howling, surrounded by magenta brushstrokes, which becomes an animated video of a dog which is at first photorealistic, and then transitions through several stages until it becomes a living painting of a stylized dog.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure14_DogMontage_Short.mp4#t=0.001\" class=\" uni-video-player__video uni-video-player__video--autoplay article-carousel__media \" title=\"Figure14_DogMontage_Short.mp4\" style=\"min-height:0px;\" autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" poster=\"\">\n             Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a download=\"\" href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/WM_Figure14_DogMontage_Short.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n            </video>\n            <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n           </div>\n          </uni-video-player>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-0\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"2y8zv\">To create Ada’s hallucination of a howling dog, we started with a concept painting by Yingzong Xin, and used Veo image-to-video to bring it to life. Veo’s first pass (without fine-tuning) was too photorealistic for our film; so we used the fine-tuned version of Veo to bring the shot closer to our intended visual style. The video-to-video workflow allowed us to switch freely between Veo and traditional tools like Premiere.</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$67653586565$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877537-0\" data-index=\"1\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877537-1\" data-index=\"2\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1769457877537-2\" data-index=\"3\"><!--?lit$67653586565$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;How animators and AI researchers made ‘Dear Upstairs Neighbors’&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"yxfsj\">Finally, to prepare our film for the big screen, we used Veo's upscaling capability to bring our final shots to 4K resolution. Guided by our artists' critique, our researchers carefully tuned the model's behavior to add rich detail that preserved every nuance of the artistic style. The Veo 4K upscaling model is available in Flow and coming to Google AI Studio and Vertex AI later this month to meet the real-world needs of filmmakers.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"4povh\">Each shot presented unique challenges, and over the course of production, our multi-disciplinary team developed several workflows combining the precise control of hand-crafted animation with the stylistic flexibility and scalability of generative AI. Not only did our AI models produce hilarious bloopers, they often surprised us with unexpectedly beautiful and creative solutions. We learned valuable lessons from coming together every day to produce each shot with fine-grained artistic intention and care. Our artists found new creative powers through direct access to experimental research, and used their craft and perspective to help shape its development. Our researchers gained hands-on experience as technical artists, rapidly prototyping solutions to break through artistic and technological barriers. We’re excited to continue our mission to build generative AI with and for professional artists and filmmakers.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google DeepMind 与资深动画专家合作创作了短片《亲爱的楼上邻居》，展示了微调后的 AI 模型和 Video-to-Video 工作流如何赋能专业动画中的艺术控制。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google DeepMind 与资深动画专家合作创作了短片《亲爱的楼上邻居》，展示了微调后的 AI 模型和 Video-to-Video 工作流如何赋能专业动画中的艺术控制。",
  "summary": "本文详细介绍了 Google DeepMind 与包括皮克斯前员工 Connie He 在内的专业动画师之间的合作项目，共同制作了名为《亲爱的楼上邻居》的动画短片。核心目标是探索如何将 Veo 和 Imagen 等生成式 AI 工具集成到高端创意工作流中，同时不牺牲艺术意图。团队在保持风格一致性和精确动作控制方面面临挑战，而传统的 Text-to-Video 模型难以解决这些问题。为此，研究人员开发了针对视觉概念的自定义微调技术以及新型 Video-to-Video 工作流，允许动画师使用粗略草图或“表演”作为 AI 生成的输入。该过程强调迭代优化、局部编辑和 4K 上采样，将 AI 视为合作伙伴而非“一键式”解决方案。这种伙伴关系让艺术家能够突破创意边界，同时也为研究人员提供了关于专业电影制作人需求的实际见解。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Text-to-video 提示词不足以满足专业叙事电影制作所需的细微差别。",
      "explanation": "单纯的文字无法传达特定的时机、面部表情或复杂的镜头构图，因此需要开发以视觉输入为引导的 Video-to-Video 工作流。"
    },
    {
      "point": "针对特定作品微调模型对于保持角色和风格的一致性至关重要。",
      "explanation": "通过从少量示例图像中向模型教授新的视觉概念，艺术家可以确保 AI 生成的内容忠实于独特的制作设计和角色设定。"
    },
    {
      "point": "专业创意领域的 AI 集成需要迭代工具，而非“一键式”生成。",
      "explanation": "制作过程涉及“样片审核”和局部优化工具，允许艺术家编辑视频的特定区域并对细节进行迭代，而无需从头开始重新生成整个镜头。"
